data.description: Incredible Opportunity in the Lewis and Clark Neighborhood of Missoula. This spacious 5 bed 3 bath home sits on a large lot and has both a one car attached garage and large detached shop/garage that can house another two vehicles, or if proper permitting could be attained, potentially be turned into an ADU. The home will need some minor cosmetic love in spots, but does have new flooring in the basement. This spacious corner lot has a fenced back yard with plenty of parking on the street and alley access. Moving into the home from the South Avenue entrance there is a living room area with brick fireplace to the right, and to the left is a dining room with built-in cabinets. Just past the living areas is the large kitchen with a stainless steel fridge and stove. The main floor boasts two bedrooms; the primary bedroom has a bath which can also be accessed from the hall as well as a walk-in closet, and the second bedroom could also act as a bright home office. The main floor is complete with a generous laundry room and two half-baths. Moving downstairs you'll notice new LVP flooring in the living areas and hall, and new carpet in the bedrooms. There is a large storage area with racks, and an area that could easily be turned into a second kitchen. It has a sink and some countertop and cabinets in it now. Tons of investment potential here. Moving down the hall is another full bath and the 3 additional bedrooms with egress. This home would make a great investment with its close proximity to the University and countless restaurants and stores, and is ideally located a short walk from Sentinel High School, Washington Middle School, Lewis and Clark Elementary, Playfair Park and Splash Montana. For more information call Jason Baker at 406-552-4443 or your real estate professional.
